OL,5, A notorious police minister during     
OL,6, white minority rule in South Africa,   
OL,7, Adriaan Vlok, has died aged 85.        
OL,9,FHe played a key role in enforcing the  
OL,10,Fracist system of apartheid, with police
OL,11,Frunning hit squads that kidnapped,     
OL,12,Ftortured and murdered activists.       
OL,14,FVlok confessed to some of his crimes   
OL,15,Fafter apartheid ended in 1994 and was  
OL,16,Fgranted amnesty.                       
OL,18,FHe also washed prominent anti-apartheid
OL,19,Fcleric Rev Frank Chikane's feet in 2006
OL,20,Fin a gesture of contrition.            
